description: The Dell Inspiron 15 3535 features a 15.6-inch display, AMD Ryzen 5 processor, 8GB RAM, and 512GB SSD, suitable for everyday computing needs.
The Dell Vostro 3510 comes with a 15.6-inch display, Intel Core i3 10th Gen processor, 8GB RAM, and 1TB HDD + 256GB SSD, ideal for business tasks.
The Dell Inspiron 15 3521 offers a 15.6-inch display, Intel Pentium Silver processor, 8GB RAM, and 256GB SSD, perfect for basic computing needs.
The Dell G15 5520 is a gaming laptop with a 15.6-inch display, Intel Core i5 12th Gen processor, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD, and NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 graphics.
The Dell Inspiron 14 5406 is a 2-in-1 laptop featuring a 14-inch touchscreen display, Intel Core i5 11th Gen processor, 8GB RAM, and 512GB SSD.
